title: Travon Walker's Debut
description:
Field Yates and the NFL Live crew discuss last nights Hall of Fame game, Travon Walker’s first game as a pro and Kevin Stefanski’s comments on the QB position for the Browns with Deshaun Watson’s suspension being appealed by the NFL.
